{"tid":434010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[咁少???] 旺角「激流」掃黃 拘8內地女","createTime":"2017-10-13T01:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T02:27:21.000Z","uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"48d70826ccae57d014b0cd5b1d2775356a8b792e","tid":434010,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:27:09.000Z","msg":"旺角警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處人員，昨午約3時展開代號「激流」（UPPERRUN）的掃黃行動，突擊搜查旺角區多棟商業及住宅大廈，拘捕共8名年齡介乎20至31歲的內地女子，涉嫌違反逗留條件，當中一人持中國護照，其餘均持雙程證。所有被捕女子現正被扣留調查，稍後將交由入境事務處跟進。"},{"pid":"b8a3e8964b9cd46ebcfae15869196ec22b9db3f1","tid":434010,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"即係有唔少係陀地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eec9599d6d75adecc1e6aceb7b8bab84ec7382","tid":434010,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係有唔少係陀地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n油麻地上海街好多企街, 一睇就知係大陸婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192b5328cb325e51c08fe32afd3429233f4bbc91","tid":434010,"uid":54436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"浪費納稅人金錢, 成30人拉8件"},{"pid":"ad65a0bcc3eea8e1fb0c7564218b8eaee630cfc9","tid":434010,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02ac67d0fcefe58d396a3d99b57ab6671f9528c5","tid":434010,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"039e9e51fbfe06b750f0bd20d906db0c681c9648","tid":434010,"uid":144774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早收到風<br />\n魚蛋無人做生意</blockquote><br />\n有黑警"},{"pid":"592bc276cce58da120a653d6d517db5338b3d3cf","tid":434010,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"